### rwkv7op的实现状态


| Framework   | cuda | triton | native |
|-------------|------|--------|--------|
| PyTorch     | ✅   | ✅     | ✅     |
| JAX         | ❌   | ✅     | ✅     | 
| TensorFlow  | ❌   | ❌     | ✅     |
| NumPy       | ❌   | ❌     | ✅     | 
